project:        Hungry Birds

description:    Examples of multi-thread and multi-process applications.

                A typical producer/consumer problem implemented with the shared
		memory model using different programming languages (C, C++,
                Java, Python, ...).

build:          GNU Autotools are used as build system for the C and C++
                implementations:
                 - autoreconf && ./configure && make
                Apache Maven is used as build system for the Java based
                implementations:
                 - mvn clean install

author:         Paolo Rovelli
contact:        paolorovelli@yahoo.it

